text: hak phwk khea thuk khab lixxk pi brrda phu klabklxk hela nan k ca mi xxk pi phrxm kab phwk khea læa tha phwk khea thuk comti brrda phu klabklxk k ca mi chwyhelux phwk khea(ya hudba ni na dir)læa hak brrda phu klabklxk chwyhelux phwk khea nænxn brrda phu klabklxk k ca phin hlang hni xxk pi phwk khea k ca mi di rab khwam chwyhelux
